30
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:07,020
Only in this way will the Wu land have a gleam of hope.

31
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:21,170
The smell of this incense is simple and elegant. It penetrates my heart.

32
00:03:21,170 --> 00:03:25,290
Even my headaches are a lot better.

33
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:31,620
Miss Wan Xiang, your fragrance indeed lives up to its reputation.

34
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,830
Thank you, City Master.

35
00:03:33,830 --> 00:03:38,520
It's just that lately I haven't been sleeping well.

36
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:42,220
There's something I've thought about over and over but still don't understand.

37
00:03:42,220 --> 00:03:46,080
I'd like to trouble you to give me an answer.

38
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:49,420
I will say all I know without reserve.

39
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:55,260
I remember you and Wan Mei entered the city at the same time.

40
00:03:55,260 --> 00:03:59,230
