43
00:04:04,270 --> 00:04:08,400
You must really hate her. Do you not?

44
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,190
Yes.

45
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:15,610
Then this is strange. That day at the Bi'an Chamber,

46
00:04:15,610 --> 00:04:19,960
