47
00:04:22,300 --> 00:04:26,020
I was temporarily confused.

48
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:31,590
Raise your head and look at me while talking.

49
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:38,780
Answer me again what I just asked you.

50
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:54,720
Master Mei! Master Mei!

51
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:57,150
Master Mei, something happened to Master Xiang!

52
00:04:57,150 --> 00:05:02,200
City Master will not let her off! I'm begging you to save her! Please, save her!

53
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:21,540
Have you determined if that is a bone from Cha Wu?

54
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:24,430
I can't be sure.

55
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:30,160
You're scared to even recognize your own mother's bones?

56
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,610
That's ridiculous.

57
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:36,310
Cha Wu isn't my mother.

58
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:42,350
If she were my mother, how could I kill her with my own hands?

59
00:05:42,350 --> 00:05:45,730
Oh? Really?

60
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:51,850
But at Chuixing Tower, when faced with my colored glass eye,

61
00:05:51,850 --> 00:05:54,120
