64
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:10,820
I was talking nonsense.

65
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,910
Consider yourself lucky.

66
00:06:16,910 --> 00:06:22,830
I think this is really your mother's leg bone.

67
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:26,420
Take a look. This sword scar on here

68
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:28,390
is precisely what she received

69
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:32,320
on her mission to Jinling seven years ago.

70
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:42,450
If you really want to prove that Cha Wu isn't your mother,

71
00:06:42,450 --> 00:06:45,240
